  - Background in software development with experience writing and shipping code to production.
  - Deep appreciation for DevX: reading API contracts, SDK interface details, and CLI flow optimization.
  - Experience with AI-native developer workflows (MCP, agents, LLM-integrated tooling). This team builds for AI as a first-class user.



