* **Job Description Summary:**
  The Senior Prompt Designer plays a defining role in shaping the quality, reliability, and evolution of MEDFAR's generative AI features — specifically "CoeurWay" (AI-powered clinical scribe) and emerging AI capabilities within MYLE EMR (Electronic Medical Record). This is a senior individual contributor role reporting to the Director of UX, with a growth path toward leading the prompt engineering practice.
* **Core Responsibilities:**
  - Audit and re-architect CoeurWay's monolithic prompts into modular, maintainable chained prompts.
  - Lead model selection, evaluation, and pairing, fostering a model-agnostic approach to optimize cost and quality.
  - Own the quality of AI-generated clinical outputs, managing hallucination risks and patient safety standards.
  - Evolve the evaluation framework covering 7 clinical note quality rubrics (aligning with ground truth and automation).
